    "attributes": {
        "action": "New rules and funding for rainwater harvesting",
        "additional_details": "We believe the Government should introduce a regulatory framework for efficient and safe rainwater harvesting, and the Government should fund public awareness campaigns.\r\n\r\nWe think this will help with water conservation, less demand for water, environmental benefits, flood mitigation, drought resilience, and financial savings for users.",
        "background": "We believe there should be incentivised installation of rainwater harvesting systems in new homes, with government funding to support this. ",
